CREATE TABLE `spider2-public-data.WWE.Cards`
(

  url STRING,
  event_id INT64,
  match_html STRING,
  event_date DATE,
  location_id INT64,
  promotion_id INT64,
  table_id INT64,
  id INT64

CREATE TABLE `spider2-public-data.WWE.Matches`
(

  card_id INT64,
  winner_id INT64,
  win_type STRING,
  loser_id INT64,
  match_type_id INT64,
  duration STRING,
  title_id INT64,
  title_change INT64
);
